snippet.title: Snow Wars - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Team up with your friends for an epic VR snowball fight in Snow Wars. Take a look at this new trailer showing off some Snow Wars gameplay, featuring the shooter's weapons, locations, and more. Snow Wars is coming to Meta Quest in October 2023.
